Quran Dalam Tatabahasa Arab: Satu Tinjauan Awal", "created_at": "2016-10-08T20:54:06.798-07:00", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/29016524/Kajian_Nilai_Shahid_al_Quran_Dalam_Tatabahasa_Arab_Satu_Tinjauan_Awal?f_ri=1275831", "dom_id": "work_29016524", "summary": "Abstrak \n\nSejak lebih tiga dekat kebelakangan ini, kajian shahid al-Quran telah mendapat tempat dalam kalangan pengkaji tatabahasa Arab sebagai usaha memahami lambakan jumlah shahid tersebut dalam karya tatabahasa. Kajian ini bermatlamat untuk menyingkap ruang kajian shahid al-Quran yang masih belum diterokai terutama dalam karya yang dihasilkan oleh tokoh tatabahasa serantau. Kertas kerja ini berbentuk kajian kualitatif dengan data utamanya diperoleh melalui analisis dokumen kepustakaan. Data sokongan pula diperoleh melalui temu bual separa struktur ke atas pentadbir dan guru yang mengajar tatabahasa Arab di tiga buah pusat pengajian pondok di Kelantan. Data-data kajian dianalisis secara deskriptif menggunakan prinsip Systematic Literature Review (SLR) bagi memenuhi objektif kajian. Hasil kajian mendapati bahawa kitab Tashil Nayl al-Amani karangan Sheikh Ahmad al-Fatani sesuai dipilih sebagai korpus kajian shahid al-Quran lanjutan memandangkan jumlah shahid al-Quran yang banyak di dalamnya. Nilai penggunaan shahid al-Quran pula boleh dijadikan fokus kajian berkenaan bagi meneroka sebab tersirat di sebalik pemilihan penggunaan shahid yang tertentu. Pendekatan kajian kualitatif pula dikesan sebagai metodologi yang sesuai kerana kajian sebegini memerlukan daya analisis dan interpretasi secara mendalam terhadap kandungan sesebuah karya tatabahasa. \n\nAbstract\n\nOver the past three decades, the study of shahid al-Quran has gained attention from Arabic grammar researchers who trying to understand the dumping of shahid in grammar works. This study aims to unveil a new field of untapped study of shahid al-Quran, especially in the work produced by the local regional grammar. This paper is a qualitative study with primary data obtained through the analysis of the document library. Support data obtained through semi-structured interviews of teachers in three traditional school (pondok) in Kelantan. The data were analyzed descriptively as it is suitable to meet the objectives of the study base on Systematics Literature Review (SLR). The study found that the book of Tashil Nayl al-Amani by Sheikh Ahmad al-Fatani suggest to be selected as corpus in next study because of the number shahid al-Quran that much in it. The value of using the Shahid al-Quran can also be the focus of the study to explore the reasons behind the choice of a particular shahid. Qualitative research approach is also detected as an appropriate methodology for this type of research as its requires in-depth analysis and interpretation of the content of a grammar works.", "downloadable_attachments": [{"id": 49466455, "asset_id": 29016524, "asset_type": "Work", "always_allow_download": false}], "ordered_authors": [{"id": 6968426, "first_name": "zamri", "last_name": "bin rajab", "domain_name": "mizanis", "page_name": "zamrirajab", "display_name": "zamri bin rajab", "profile_url": "https://mizanis.academia.edu/zamrirajab?f_ri=1275831", "photo": "https://0.academia-photos.com/6968426/2685835/3322257/s65_zamri.rajab.jpg"}], "research_interests": [{"id": 1200807, "name": "Shahid al-Quran", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Shahid_al-Quran?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1200811, "name": "Tatabahasa Arab", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Tatabahasa_Arab?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1275831, "name": "Sheikh Ahmad Al-Fatani", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Sheikh_Ahmad_Al-Fatani?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1694181, "name": "Ulama Nusantara", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Ulama_Nusantara?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 2018662, "name": "Kitab Tashil Nayl Al-Amani", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Kitab_Tashil_Nayl_Al-Amani?f_ri=1275831"}]}, {"id": 12261583, "title": "Shahid al-Quran Dalam Kitab Tashil Nayl Al-Amani Karya Sheikh Ahmad Al-Fatani", "created_at": "2015-05-06T05:41:01.164-07:00", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/12261583/Shahid_al_Quran_Dalam_Kitab_Tashil_Nayl_Al_Amani_Karya_Sheikh_Ahmad_Al_Fatani?f_ri=1275831", "dom_id": "work_12261583", "summary": "Fatani termasyhur sebagai sebuah daerah di Selatan Thailand yang telah melahirkan ramai tokoh cendikiawan Islam terulung di Nusantara. Sheikh Wan Ahmad bin Muhammad Zain Al-Fatani (Sheikh Ahmad) dilihat menyinar dengan tersohornya karya-karya karangan beliau dalam pelbagai disiplin ilmu khususnya tatabahasa Arab melalui kitab Tashil Nayl Al-Amani fi Sharh cAwamil Al-Jurjani (Tashil). Kajian ini bermatlamat untuk mengetengahkan usaha Sheikh Ahmad yang banyak menggunakan shahid al-Quran dalam karyanya tersebut sehingga telah menyumbang kepada perkembangan pengajaran dan pembelajaran ilmu tatabahasa Arab bukan sahaja di Nusantara bahkan ke seluruh dunia Islam. Kajian ini berbentuk kajian kualitatif dengan menggunakan kaedah analisis dokumen. Hasil kajian menunjukkan bahawa Sheikh Ahmad mempunyai sifat-sifat peribadi yang murni, mengikuti pelbagai disiplin ilmu, aktif dalam bidang penulisan ilmu-ilmu yang dikuasainya dan dikesan mengaplikasi shahid al-Quran secara komprehensif dalam amalan pengajaran dan pembelajaran tatabahasa Arab khususnya melalui kitab Tashil. Kajian ini menzahirkan keperibadian Sheikh Ahmad dan sumbangan emas beliau boleh diiktiraf sebagai bitara dalam matra tatabahasa Arab Nusantara seluruhnya.", "downloadable_attachments": [{"id": 37557884, "asset_id": 12261583, "asset_type": "Work", "always_allow_download": false}], "ordered_authors": [{"id": 6968426, "first_name": "zamri", "last_name": "bin rajab", "domain_name": "mizanis", "page_name": "zamrirajab", "display_name": "zamri bin rajab", "profile_url": "https://mizanis.academia.edu/zamrirajab?f_ri=1275831", "photo": "https://0.academia-photos.com/6968426/2685835/3322257/s65_zamri.rajab.jpg"}], "research_interests": [{"id": 1200807, "name": "Shahid al-Quran", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Shahid_al-Quran?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1200811, "name": "Tatabahasa Arab", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Tatabahasa_Arab?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1275831, "name": "Sheikh Ahmad Al-Fatani", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Sheikh_Ahmad_Al-Fatani?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1924721, "name": "Tashil Nayl Al-Amani", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Tashil_Nayl_Al-Amani?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow": false}]}, {"id": 12086802, "title": "Muslims in Thailand: A Bibliography of English-language Scholarship", "created_at": "2015-04-23T18:55:18.419-07:00", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/12086802/Muslims_in_Thailand_A_Bibliography_of_English_language_Scholarship?f_ri=1275831", "dom_id": "work_12086802", "summary": "While running the risk of stating the obvious, this is a bibliography English-language scholarship dealing with Thailand's Muslim minority", "downloadable_attachments": [{"id": 37406351, "asset_id": 12086802, "asset_type": "Work", "always_allow_download": false}], "ordered_authors": [{"id": 667449, "first_name": "Christopher", "last_name": "Joll", "domain_name": "victoria", "page_name": "ChristopherJoll", "display_name": "Christopher M Joll", "profile_url": "https://victoria.academia.edu/ChristopherJoll?f_ri=1275831", "photo": "https://0.academia-photos.com/667449/851788/1060921/s65_cm.joll.jpg"}], "research_interests": [{"id": 1031, "name": "Southeast Asian Studies", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Southeast_Asian_Studies?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1234, "name": "Thai Studies", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Thai_Studies?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1660, "name": "Terrorism", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Terrorism?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow"