nts/in/Violence_in_South_Thailand?f_ri=1275831"}, {"id": 952327, "name": "Southeast Asian Islam", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Southeast_Asian_Islam?f_ri=1275831"}, {"id": 961753, "name": "Malay World Studies", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Malay_World_Studies?f_ri=1275831"}, {"id": 961759, "name": "Indonesia and the Malay World", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Indonesia_and_the_Malay_World?f_ri=1275831"}, {"id": 991397, "name": "Deep South of Thailand", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Deep_South_of_Thailand?f_ri=1275831"}, {"id": 1002942, "name": "Indian Ocean Region", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Indian_Ocean_Region?f_ri=1275831"}, {"id": 1006531, "name": "Malay World and Malay Studies", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Malay_World_and_Malay_Studies?f_ri=1275831"}, {"id": 1015170, "name": "The Malay World", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/The_Malay_World?f_ri=1275831"}, {"id": 1275829, "name": "Sheikh Daud Al-Fatani", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Sheikh_Daud_Al-Fatani?f_ri=1275831"}, {"id": 1275831, "name": "Sheikh Ahmad Al-Fatani", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Sheikh_Ahmad_Al-Fatani?f_ri=1275831"}, {"id": 1375815, "name": "Patani", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Patani?f_ri=1275831"}]}, {"id": 27198488, "title": "Shahid al-Quran In Arabic Grammar Works: A Systematic Literature Review (Shahid Al-Quran Dalam Karya Tatabahasa Arab: Satu Sorotan Literatur Secara Sistematik)", "created_at": "2016-07-23T04:30:19.744-07:00", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/27198488/Shahid_al_Quran_In_Arabic_Grammar_Works_A_Systematic_Literature_Review_Shahid_Al_Quran_Dalam_Karya_Tatabahasa_Arab_Satu_Sorotan_Literatur_Secara_Sistematik_?f_ri=1275831", "dom_id": "work_27198488", "summary": "The Theory of Nahu al-Quran which emphasizes on the impact of using Koran in Arabic grammar has attracted a lot of research. Within 31 years after the emergence of this theory (1984-2015), there were over 19 studies that used the term shahid al-Quran either in research conducted to qualify for an academic certificate, articles published in journals or seminar papers. This qualitative study aims to explore the literature review of shahid al-Quran through document analysis and the matrix of Systematic Literature Review (SLR). In doing so, a systematic analysis is conducted on the background, issues or gap pertaining to this study as well as methodology and findings on previous research. This study has found that the study of shahid al-Quran was popular among Arab researchers especially on the major works written by Arabic scholars and the qualitative study using content analysis technic was the most preferred method chosen by these researchers. The studies on Shahid al-Quran should continue and develop to explore both the obvious and the underlying reasons behind its usage among scholars of Arabic grammar. Arab, the theory of nahu al-Quran, systematic literature review. ABSTRAK Teori Nahu al-Quran yang menekankan impak al-Quran dalam tatabahasa Arab telah menarik banyak kajian dilakukan. Dalam tempoh 31 tahun selepas munculnya teori tersebut (1984-2015), terdapat lebih 19 kajian menggunakan istilah shahid al-Quran dihasilkan sama ada kajian bagi memenuhi syarat memperoleh ijazah akademik, artikel yang diterbitkan dalam jurnal mahupun kertas seminar. Kajian kualitatif ini meninjau literatur kajian shahid al-Quran dengan menggunakan kaedah analisis dokumen dan berpandukan jadual matrik \" Systematic Literature Review (SLR) \". Analisis sistematik berkenaan memfokuskan kepada latar belakang, isu atau lompang, metodologi dan dapatan kajian. Hasil kajian mendapati kajian shahid al-Quran telah popular dalam kalangan pengkaji Arab dengan fokus kepada karya utama karangan ulama tatabahasa berketurunan Arab, manakala bentuk kajian kualitatif menggunakan kaedah analisis dokumen atau kandungan lebih mendominasi kajian shahid al-Quran. Kajian shahid al-Quran perlu terus dikembangkan seperti meneroka sebab yang tersurat dan tersirat di sebalik penggunaannya dalam kalangan sarjana tatabahasa. Kata kunci: shahid al-Quran, tatabahasa Arab, teori nahu al-Quran, sorotan literatur secara sistematik.", "downloadable_attachments": [{"id": 47451732, "asset_id": 27198488, "asset_type": "Work", "always_allow_download": false}], "ordered_authors": [{"id": 6968426, "first_name": "zamri", "last_name": "bin rajab", "domain_name": "mizanis", "page_name": "zamrirajab", "display_name": "zamri bin rajab", "profile_url": "https://mizanis.academia.edu/zamrirajab?f_ri=1275831", "photo": "https://0.academia-photos.com/6968426/2685835/3322257/s65_zamri.rajab.jpg"}], "research_interests": [{"id": 6482, "name": "Meta-Analysis and Systematic Review", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Meta-Analysis_and_Systematic_Review?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 66683, "name": "Systematic Literature Review", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Systematic_Literature_Review?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1200807, "name": "Shahid al-Quran", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Shahid_al-Quran?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1200811, "name": "Tatabahasa Arab", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Tatabahasa_Arab?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1275831, "name": "Sheikh Ahmad Al-Fatani", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Sheikh_Ahmad_Al-Fatani?f_ri=1275831"}, {"id": 2018662, "name": "Kitab Tashil Nayl Al-Amani", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Kitab_Tashil_Nayl_Al-Amani?f_ri=1275831"}]}, {"id": 14458481, "title": "Shahid Al-Quran in Kitab Tashil Nayl Al-Amani by Sheikh Ahmad Al-Fatani", "created_at": "2015-07-28T03:22:08.668-07:00", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/14458481/Shahid_Al_Quran_in_Kitab_Tashil_Nayl_Al_Amani_by_Sheikh_Ahmad_Al_Fatani?f_ri=1275831", "dom_id": "work_14458481", "summary": "Fatani is a famous region in the south Thailand, which had produced many Islamic scholars in its country. Sheikh Wan Ahmad bin Muhammad Zain Al-Fatani (Sheikh Ahmad) seems known with his writings in variety of disciplines, especially through the book of Arabic grammar Tashil Nayl Al-Amani fi Sharh \u2018Awamil Al-Jurjani (Tashil). This study aims to highlight the efforts of Sheikh Ahmad which used many shahid al-Quran in his writings and had contributed them to the development of teaching and learning Arabic grammar not only in its country but to the entire Islamic world. This study is a qualitative using documentary analysis. The results showed that Sheikh Ahmad has his own personal characteristics that are pure, follow various disciplines of knowledge, active in the fields of writing, which he controls and able to trace used of shahid al-Quran in a comprehensive manner in order to practice of teaching and learning the Arabic grammar, especially through the kitab Tashil. This study discloses the personality of Sheikh Ahmad and his gold contribution can be recognized as a niche in the whole archipelago dimension Arabic grammar", "downloadable_attachments": [{"id": 38314641, "asset_id": 14458481, "asset_type": "Work", "always_allow_download": false}], "ordered_authors": [{"id": 6968426, "first_name": "zamri", "last_name": "bin rajab", "domain_name": "mizanis", "page_name": "zamrirajab", "display_name": "zamri bin rajab", "profile_url": "https://mizanis.academia.edu/zamrirajab?f_ri=1275831", "photo": "https://0.academia-photos.com/6968426/2685835/3322257/s65_zamri.rajab.jpg"}], "research_interests": [{"id": 1200807, "name": "Shahid al-Quran", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Shahid_al-Quran?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1200811, "name": "Tatabahasa Arab", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Tatabahasa_Arab?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1216746, "name": "Sarjana Tatabahasa Arab", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Sarjana_Tatabahasa_Arab?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1275831, "name": "Sheikh Ahmad Al-Fatani", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Sheikh_Ahmad_Al-Fatani?f_ri=1275831", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1924721, "name": "Tashil Nayl Al-Amani", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Tashil_Nayl_Al-Amani?f_ri=1275831"}]}]